article_title: ETSU’s Alpha Delta Pi to hold Ronald McDonald House Benefit and Auction

og.description: The Gamma Phi Chapter of Alpha Delta Pi Sorority at East Tennessee State University and the sorority’s East Tennessee Alumnae Association will hold Roarin’ for Ronald, the 14th Annual Benefit and Auction for the Southern Appalachian Ronald McDonald House April 9, at 6:30 p.m. in the King’s Centre at 300 E. Main St.
